GP, I am glad to see you are here, a friendly face from close by. I am
also glad to see that this site is not all negative.  I had just
joined last week, and made the post about the Door to the Dead; and
with all the negative post was thinking about leaving this forum. In
fact I had e-mailed Larry privately expressing that thought.

I have seen a rash of e-mails more up beat so I have gone back to
individual e-mails from the digest.  I think I will hang around a
little longer.

For other members in Texas, I&#39;m in Houston, just across the channel
from the Golden Phoenix.  I see we are well represented as a state. I
am glad to meet all of you.


Regards,
Jon in Texas


